			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) kill Lorroakan at  CTY_Main_A 4960; 0; 705\r\n2) Kill Rolan when he appears at the scene\r\n3) Go through any portal that is not the left one on the second floor of Ramazith at -1; 30; -97 (and revive yourself)\r\n4) call oe LOW_SorcerousSundries_AradinLeaveAndAttack in recon\r\n5)  ctrl+shift+k Klank at -15; 26; -68\r\n6) attempt to enter the shop, getting interrupted"
				},
